      "content": "i tried the breathing thing but it didn't really do much, the heaviness is still there. honestly i get these panic attacks all the time and they usually feel the same way. do u think it's worth me calling an ambulance or is it more likely just my anxiety acting up again? i dont want to make a big deal out of nothing if it's just stress.",
