      "content": "i'm just so tired of the hospital trips and the sirens, it's so stressful and honestly makes my anxiety way worse. my doctor did say last time that these sensations are very common with my type of anxiety. if i just take one of my prescribed diazepam pills i'll probably just sleep it off and feel better in the morning, right? that's better than a whole trip to A&E for nothing.",
